      • createSuitableXmlRoot

        private static InputStream createSuitableXmlRoot​(InputStream inputStream)
        Add a root node to create a valid XML Document. Since instance files are XML like files, without a root node, we need to create a root node. With that, we can leave the XML parsing part to a dedicated library with a better support than an hand-made one. Thanks to https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6640756/parsing-an-xml-stream-with-no-root-element for the code to sandwich an InputStream
        Parameters:
        inputStream - Stream to sandwich
        Returns:
        A valid and well formed document
